 @{u}MODEL@{uu}: COM-1

 @{u}RANGE@{uu}: 2.08x10^14 km

 @{u}TELEMETRY/CHANNELS@{uu}: 215,634

 @{u}BUOY FEATURES@{uu}:
   standard package
   beta sensor package
   communication software
   fempto second data collection
   high gain antenna
   interstellar communication
